\b0 \cf0  
\fs20 7:35:43 pm
\fs26 \
\pard\pardeftab720

\b \cf0 C++ and Python have rules for all of this, but Java simplifies things by only allowing you to extend one superclass.
\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720

\b \cf2 dkneezel
\b0 \cf0  
\fs20 7:35:51 pm
